import HttpClientModule into app.module.ts

1. create a task interface
list all important datatypes

2. create task component
.ts file has an @input of type Itask
.html file is a card with {{task.data_name}}

3. create task service
import httpClient into constructor
import Itask
create a get and a post function

4. add-task page
create form in .html
import ReactiveFormsModule into add-task.module.ts
add-task.page.ts has a function add_task() which is where you need to call the createTask() function from the taskService

5. in tab1 page to show the tasks:
import task component into tab1 routing module, add to declarations and to exports
in tab1.page.ts import task service, oninit into constructor along with a subscribe function
in .html file, add a div to show all  tasks using *ngFor  

